I don't care if he likes Volkswagens.

00:03:21.968 --> 00:03:24.037
You know,
he could be a Chevy guy or anything,

00:03:24.037 --> 00:03:28.541
but maybe we have to start looking
as teachers and educators that

00:03:28.841 --> 00:03:32.045
not everybody's going to read Shakespeare,
but everybody can read and can.

